{"tid":202870,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"飲完牛奶肚痛，思考緊人生哲學","createTime":"2017-04-15T22:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T00:34:36.000Z","uid":36374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a46b45a95086be2018a8654eaea811096cb51ea9","tid":202870,"uid":36374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:04:31.000Z","msg":"坐緊係馬桶，諗緊一個問題。<br />\n假如我舊黃金出到一半，呢個時候作嘔。<br />\n<br />\n咁我應該起身嘔落馬桶到，然後舊黃金跌落地。<br />\n定係繼續屙，然後嘔落地下到？<br />\n<br />\n呃求巴打解答，可能陣間要做決定<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘔落地下到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘔落馬桶到"},{"pid":"e1c52e4a50389c9081cb7eef142cc1443ac417b4","tid":202870,"uid":76883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:06:10.000Z","msg":"吞咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2fd5351e512237b0c3fdd8120f4abb239fb13b","tid":202870,"uid":1274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:09:27.000Z","msg":"正路就睇下隔離有無刷牙水杯，裝嘔吐物，<br />\n<br />\nbtw屌你老母個post好撚核突"},{"pid":"fb0275276a4aa7bf4768485bf92c1723e7b65299","tid":202870,"uid":45844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:11:12.000Z","msg":"一定係嘔落馬桶，一舊屎點都易清潔過嘔吐物。<br />\n除非你好似我依家咁屙緊爛屎。<br />\n所以我負左你皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db1770a313bfaf4b398896469c48dfedd791a7f","tid":202870,"uid":5007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:22:02.000Z","msg":"未試過腸胃炎又屙又嘔？<br />\n坐屎塔 手拎水桶/膠袋"},{"pid":"5dafd8a3867a4214c1d26141bad009dd344e7b1c","tid":202870,"uid":5007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:24:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未試過腸胃炎又屙又嘔？<br />\n坐屎塔 手拎水桶/膠袋</blockquote><br />\n如果無腸胃炎 應該都無咩機會屙緊無啦啦急嘔<br />\n正常你都忍到幾秒 幾秒夠你cut斷條屎再洗手盤嘔完先屙"},{"pid":"bde7f4819e911901b39c6d9ee38ddfb12a6bedf9","tid":202870,"uid":6310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"